quran[3]{c,v,t,f}:
  2,16,"Jamanjao ni aŵalaŵala ŵasagwile kusokonechela pakusumanya ni chongoko, nambo kusumanya kwaoko nganikwajonjechesya (chilichose), soni nganaŵa ŵakongoka."
  2,17,"Chilandanyo chao chili chisawu ajulajula jwana kolesyaga moto (ndema jajwaliji nkwenda nchipi), sano katema kawalangwisye yayaliji mungulugulu mwakwe, Allah ŵatyochesye lilanguka lyaolyo, nikwaleka ali nchipi ŵangaŵa nkulola."
  2,18,"Ŵangapikana, ŵangaŵecheta, ŵangalola soni nganaŵa awujile (kuchongoko)."